NYC Executive Summary 2019
> 200 stages through NYC
> 50,000 seats over 3 main categories:  Broadway, Off-Broadway, Off-Off Broadway

748 small venue organizations
600 production companies
97 producing or presenting organizations
51 theater organizations under umbrella of larger institution

workers:
- actors
- playwrights
- designers
- creative teams
- craftspeople

small venue theater industry:
$1.3 billion in econonmic output
8,400 full-time equivalent jobs
$512 million in wages in 2017

small theater economic multiplier
2.2 (vs 1.55 for other media and enterainment organizations)

